data.name: labelRepetierInfo.Text
data.value: This software was developed for controlling RepRap like 3D-printer. It is best used with Repetier-Firmware, which supports all features. Other printer firmware like Teacup, Sprinter or 5D GCode interpreter should work with proper settings.
